The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves algorithm design for welfare maximization problems, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the computational model of Bernoulli factories, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG).
